Description: Functions for using the 'StreamCat' and 'LakeCat' API and interacting with the
             'StreamCat' and 'LakeCat' database. Convenience functions in the package wrap
             the API for 'StreamCat' on <https://api.epa.gov/StreamCat/streams/metrics>.
